Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,========OPJP=========
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.55,0:01:18.52,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}泣きじゃくりながら旅をしてた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.91,0:01:23.35,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}せめてこの宇宙（そら）を飛べるのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.35,0:01:29.22,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喧嘩した夜は星が優しい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.63,0:01:34.20,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}キミも見ているかな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:40.19,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}シラナイ…シリタイ…カンジタイ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:47.73,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}なんにもないなら　なんにでもなれるはず
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.71,0:01:51.22,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}その時 生まれたときめきが
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.51,0:01:53.89,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}時空の波サーフしてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.21,0:01:59.08,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不思議だね　今なら怖くない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:02.00,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}未完成なまま　飛び込もう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.34,0:02:04.87,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}約束の扉（ドア）を開けて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.87,0:02:09.60,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}まぶしい笑顔になれ！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.96,0:00:00.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,========OPCN=========
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.55,0:01:18.52,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}抽泣着走在旅途上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.91,0:01:23.35,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}若至少要是能在这片宇宙中翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.35,0:01:29.22,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吵架后的夜晚繁星是如此温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.63,0:01:34.20,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是不是也在看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:40.19,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么都不知道…想要去了解…想要去感受…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:47.73,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果一无所有 那么反而能化身一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.71,0:01:51.22,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个时候心中的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.51,0:01:53.89,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}乘着时空的巨浪飞了出去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.21,0:01:59.08,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真不可思议 现在的我无所畏惧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:02.00,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}保持不成熟的自己就这么冲过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.34,0:02:04.87,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}打开那扇约定的大门
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.87,0:02:09.60,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}露出耀眼的笑容
Comment: 0,0:02:26.87,0:02:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,======text=====
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs98\b1\pos(470,920)\bord0}流星预报： 雨时有流星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.82,0:02:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔…嘿咻…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.61,0:02:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.17,0:02:43.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪啊 该不会是丢了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.63,0:02:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50\fn方正大标宋_GBK\blur1.5\bord1.5}天文爱好会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.63,0:02:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs50\fn方正大标宋_GBK\blur1.5\bord1.5}秋天的英仙座 来看流星雨吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.97,0:02:46.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊好疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.84,0:02:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真疼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.76,0:02:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.15,0:03:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.67,0:03:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不换身衣服？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我只是回来取望远镜的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.55,0:03:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着又去学校？一直放学校不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.58,0:03:19.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不过…这是很重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.14,0:03:23.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也对 一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.12,0:03:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来时要不要让你父亲去接你？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:27.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.49,0:03:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.76,0:03:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说葵！不要边走边看书！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.67,0:03:47.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还给我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:50.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好险好险 还好你遇到的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.74,0:03:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了啦 不会再边走边看了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.68,0:03:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗？这都第几次了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的！所以快还给我啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.21,0:03:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.66,0:04:02.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来紧靠在一起的闪烁明星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.51,0:04:08.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实一颗颗都远远相距着好几光年
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.74,0:04:12.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在空无一物的宇宙里独自闪耀着的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.66,0:04:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定她们同样也在仰望着繁星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坚信着总有一天其光辉将会传达给某人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.96,0:04:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.50,0:04:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天预报有流星雨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:31.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在这种夜晚里 仰望星空 肩靠着肩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.51,0:04:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起倾听繁星们那好似低语般的光辉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.72,0:04:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跻身于那互相依偎的闪耀繁星之中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.37,0:05:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.15,0:05:35.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是有客人来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:38.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪不得天空如此喧嚣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.30,0:05:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.90,0:05:58.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问 你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.54,0:06:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很轻吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:08.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 刚才发出了奇怪的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:09.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.69,0:06:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到那边去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.88,0:06:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边是哪边？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.43,0:06:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法突然停下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 赶不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.37,0:06:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 到底该怎么办才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.21,0:06:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:31.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,镜头保护镜…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:34.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只坏了这个真是不幸中的万幸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.46,0:06:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这人 一直做事不得要领
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.55,0:06:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连朋友也经常说我慢吞吞的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.21,0:06:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.49,0:06:54.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它叫什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:57.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔 我也不清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.74,0:07:02.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 无论有多美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但只能在这里活下去的事物你觉得有意义吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:07.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.08,0:07:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好比再璀璨的光辉只要不被人看到 便与黑暗无异
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.57,0:07:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该有上锁的 这不是谁都能来的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昴 我叫昴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.87,0:07:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵 不是问你名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.06,0:07:32.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昴 你没有看见星星吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.09,0:07:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星星？啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.20,0:07:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了！我必须得走了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.49,0:07:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那个…今晚有流星雨 我非常想看…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.59,0:07:53.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 方便的话…不来一起看流星雨吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:03.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯 肯定…肯定会很漂亮的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.87,0:08:05.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.53,0:08:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊讨厌 超羞人的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.84,0:08:20.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得去瞭望室了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:23.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？但是这里应该是瞭望室…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我难道做了场梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:27.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.21,0:08:38.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可看不到星星啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.32,0:08:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊受不了 难喝 真难喝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们到底欠缺什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再有一个人的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你这么说 救世主也不会这么凑巧出现的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.37,0:08:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的运势如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.16,0:09:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七号是幸运 美妙的邂逅在等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是处女座的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天秤座
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.51,0:09:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是你自己的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今就算再增加一人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.43,0:09:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是个适合可爱洋服的女孩子就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.99,0:09:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是个慢吞到无药可救的家伙该怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.69,0:09:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 我们要在这呆到什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.52,0:09:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到会长回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会长？我们进了什么会？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.01,0:09:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进展到什么程度了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:26.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算下雨也并不代表星星消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.15,0:09:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.46,0:09:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是这么说 我根本没带伞啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.87,0:09:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.35,0:10:00.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的指南针！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的到底是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.21,0:10:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,软趴趴的 也不凉 还有点暖暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.99,0:10:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 难不成…是妖怪！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.44,0:10:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昴…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.04,0:00:01.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昴？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.35,0:10:53.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么？认识的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！哎哎哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.03,0:11:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.54,0:11:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么小葵在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么昴在这里啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.72,0:11:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昴 你能看见我？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.05,0:11:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这身打扮…真可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:20.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可 可爱什么的 你这人真失礼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.54,0:11:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊呀 本来就可爱嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.83,0:11:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是完全没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如说还很中意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:30.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没 没什么啦！和昴无关！从头到脚一点关系都没！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:34.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美妙的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.99,0:11:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 奈奈子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.20,0:11:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我们的救世主？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么呀 不愧是小葵 有所隐瞒可不好喵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.19,0:11:44.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我等等 昴做不来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.79,0:11:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,门打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也看见我们了 不会有错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,0:11:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.85,0:11:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.33,0:12:00.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那个 是我的指南针
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.79,0:12:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂停暂停
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许对会长动粗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会长？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 昴宿星团星人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.97,0:12:09.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昴宿星团？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.90,0:12:14.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能从你身上感到巨大的力量 请务必协助我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.71,0:12:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不行的 昴做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.89,0:12:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚程又短动作又慢 没有我就什么都决定不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.42,0:12:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不是小葵你自顾自决定的！我明明什么都没拜托你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:32.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:34.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.55,0:12:38.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.76,0:12:40.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.05,0:12:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能听见吗？昴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.96,0:12:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？嗯 时不时能听到这种…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好耶 回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦说中了 流星预报 雨有时有流星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.93,0:12:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真少见 话说这是第一次吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.71,0:12:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流星？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.76,0:13:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 非常漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 下着雨…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:04.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事影响不了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.57,0:13:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.61,0:13:20.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到人挺性急的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.30,0:13:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧你干了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.25,0:13:26.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:41.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中注意到传动轴上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.71,0:14:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为昴你慌慌张张的那孩子也平静不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.51,0:14:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传动轴？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是怎么回事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.01,0:14:50.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的这个 是哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.59,0:14:51.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:53.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来了 葵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.99,0:14:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 挺合身的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.82,0:14:56.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:14:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我们在飞？这身衣服是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.05,0:15:01.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底发生什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.76,0:15:03.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一股脑问过来我也不好回答啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.31,0:15:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.11,0:15:39.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是碎片 引擎的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引擎？碎片？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 会长的宇宙飞船的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会长？宇宙飞船？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要让我一次次重复
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.47,0:15:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 要怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.52,0:15:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住它
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.46,0:15:50.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁抓？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.57,0:15:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.12,0:15:54.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一次 能成功吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:15:58.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 这次一定要成功
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 那孩子交给你可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.37,0:16:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.93,0:16:04.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昴 我叫昴！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:05.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我叫光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:07.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边的是奈奈子和树
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.62,0:16:08.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.15,0:16:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那身和适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.73,0:16:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昴你什么都不用做 跟好我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.93,0:16:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 这个是什么？我们为什么在飞？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.34,0:16:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼下不要想有的没的了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.06,0:16:23.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制服也变成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事之后再问也行啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.73,0:16:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事是哪种事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.69,0:16:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用知道 和昴你无关
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:34.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都不知道 办不到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:36.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么小葵在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵你明明丢下我去了别的学校才对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.61,0:16:46.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么呢！丢下我的难道不是昴吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.76,0:16:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:49.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.54,0:16:51.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.34,0:16:55.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们瞎搞什么呢 两个人都集中注意了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.30,0:16:56.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.19,0:17:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.47,0:17:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂停暂停暂停！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.35,0:17:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在发生什么 我也不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.56,0:17:36.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵 你为什么在做这种事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要改变
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我 没能改变自身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.71,0:17:51.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昴难道不是吗？昴不是做出改变了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不太明白 但是那样的话 肯定是不同的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.71,0:18:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 净是些搞不明白的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.56,0:18:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改变得了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.27,0:18:05.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那什么 眼下改变了的还只是衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.03,0:18:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.14,0:18:11.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及 稍微能使点魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.56,0:18:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 就算是这样昴你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.88,0:18:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.19,0:18:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底明不明白我们在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.68,0:18:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.60,0:18:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不明白怎么可能做得…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.00,0:18:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵你不是刚才也说了不明白吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.97,0:18:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊呀 刚才那句说到点上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.93,0:18:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这一点我们也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.65,0:18:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说了也还没成功回收过碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.75,0:18:38.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.79,0:18:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.90,0:18:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.26,0:18:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们 正准备去做谁都不曾尝试过的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.11,0:18:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有去做的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.62,0:18:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵能做到的话我肯定也能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.82,0:18:56.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会变成那样啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:18:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 走吧 再试一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真少见啊 树竟然会那样说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:08.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我感觉现在的话就能做到 不去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.28,0:19:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只限今天 今天！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.19,0:19:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是引擎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.38,0:19:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 为了把会长送回母星所需要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.76,0:19:25.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs72}我所乘坐的恒星间宇宙飞船 在地球时间的七年前发生了事故
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.86,0:19:28.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当时四分五裂了的引擎的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.89,0:19:31.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能飞得到那边吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.82,0:19:33.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来有4千米
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.73,0:19:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有去了不是吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.71,0:19:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要放手哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.07,0:19:38.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.00,0:19:42.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们应该也已经相当累了 没有下个机会了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.77,0:19:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.39,0:19:45.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟肚子都饿扁了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.39,0:19:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 该怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.82,0:19:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利用魔法阵 来关闭碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.39,0:19:51.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关闭？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.24,0:19:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔…就是停止的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.83,0:19:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.73,0:19:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不是奈奈子这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:20:00.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为英语的抽象概念来得丰富…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.57,0:20:02.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要放手了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.40,0:20:03.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.65,0:20:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 很安定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.84,0:20:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管发生什么都不要放开传动轴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.05,0:20:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.10,0:20:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何如何？抓到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.39,0:20:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我们的干扰波捕捉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害 5个人话就能变得这么安定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.66,0:20:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.23,0:20:28.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先保持这样让其简并
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.24,0:20:29.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简并？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.12,0:20:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前不是刚教过你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.17,0:20:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没试过哪知道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.35,0:20:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变小了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.56,0:20:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后只要令其确定化的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.44,0:20:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.01,0:20:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.81,0:20:47.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昴 不要开小差！哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.83,0:20:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色的流星？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.51,0:20:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:55.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.07,0:20:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.23,0:20:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是什么？哇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！嘿呀！看招！不要躲！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.09,0:21:05.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好！结界要解开了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:12.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碎片！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.31,0:21:15.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.47,0:21:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好！令其确定化了！…不对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.48,0:21:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃 昴！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.53,0:21:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.65,0:21:25.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小昴！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.71,0:21:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开碎片！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.29,0:21:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行！大家好不容易抓到的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.14,0:21:32.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不用管那么多！快放手！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.49,0:21:33.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.35,0:21:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撞上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.49,0:21:44.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害！我连擦都擦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.84,0:21:45.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.91,0:21:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.81,0:21:52.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也太慢吞了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.68,0:21:54.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我叫昴…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.24,0:21:55.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没问你名字！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.07,0:21:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.37,0:21:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管好你自己吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.52,0:21:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.56,0:22:00.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的了！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.56,0:22:03.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不！是我们的！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.23,0:22:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.01,0:22:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙到底是什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.76,0:22:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也完全没头绪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.30,0:22:16.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来…像个男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.27,0:22:24.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昴 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.15,0:22:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.58,0:22:30.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.64,0:22:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会错的 虽然很小但这的确是宇宙飞船引擎的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.50,0:22:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.38,0:22:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了！我们的初次成果！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.12,0:22:40.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是和黑家伙撞上的时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.89,0:22:44.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定小昴果真是我们的救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.07,0:22:51.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是流星雨…流星雨啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.59,0:22:56.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本以为今夜会看不到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.97,0:23:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}待续
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.04,0:00:01.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.28,0:23:23.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能看到流星雨真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.48,0:23:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.22,0:23:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那什么 从今往后请多关照 小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.03,0:23:30.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我才是 昴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.96,0:23:32.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 巡星之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.88,0:23:34.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你们俩那么清纯？
